- DQN 학습 환경 구축 및 ROS2-Gym 연동

📂 프로젝트 구조
~/ros2_ws/src/tb3_rl/
├── package.xml
├── setup.py
├── worlds/training_arena.wbt
├── controllers/episode_supervisor/episode_supervisor.py
└── tb3_rl/
    ├── tb3_env.py
    ├── train_dqn.py
    ├── run_dqn.py

⚙️ 의존성 설치
pip install torch==2.2.2+cpu torchvision==0.17.2+cpu torchaudio==2.2.2+cpu -f https://download.pytorch.org/whl/torch_stable.html
pip install "numpy<2" --force-reinstall
pip install gym stable-baselines3 matplotlib

✅ 환경 빌드 및 확인
cd ~/ros2_ws
colcon build
source ~/ros2_ws/install/setup.bash

🧭 Webots 환경 실행
webots ~/ros2_ws/src/tb3_rl/worlds/training_arena.wbt
